  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to identify the efficacy of virtual visitation in Intensive Care&#xD;
      Unit on patients and their caregivers during COVID-19 Pandemic.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      After being informed about the study, all patients who meet the eligibility requirements will&#xD;
      be randomized in a 1:1 ratio to intervention group (Virtual visitation once a day) or Control&#xD;
      group (Phone interviews once a day).&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
